title: HURUC Corner Shower Caddy – 2 Pack Rustproof, Bathroom Corner Shelves, No-Drill Adhesive, Suction for Accessories and Storage, Black (Black)
features: Durable High-Quality Material: Built with premium-grade materials, the HURUC Corner Shower Caddy is designed to withstand daily use and maintain its sturdiness over time, ensuring long-lasting performance.

Space-Saving Corner Design: Optimize your bathroom space with this sleek and modern corner caddy, perfect for holding all your shower essentials like shampoo, soap, and accessories in a tidy and accessible way.

Strong Adhesive, No-Drill Installation: Features a heavy-duty adhesive system for quick and easy installation without the need for drilling, keeping your walls intact while securely holding up to 40kg.
Water-Resistant and Easy to Maintain: The water-resistant design ensures durability and prevents damage from moisture, while the open-frame construction allows for proper drainage and easy cleaning.
Stylish and Versatile: Combining functionality and elegance, this shower caddy fits seamlessly into any bathroom decor, making it ideal for apartments, dorms, or homes of all sizes.
